				p(style="font-size:16px") The second “Inspire Innovation-Sony China（IISC）” business innovation event has officially kicked off in SCN.

				p(style="font-size:16px") Last year, to explore those potential new business and take roots in China, SCN’s IISC project committee introduced the "bottom-up" innovation proposal mechanism into China. Based on a series of introduction activities, 69 projects from 16 departments participated in the first IISC in 2016 totally. 40 projects won the opportunity to take exhibitions in Shanghai and Beijing office, and 9 projects won awards from company management.
				br
				p(style="font-size:16px") This year, in order to give participant an opportunity to communicate with certain departments adequately, and to go all out to help the projects applied to business practice and make practical benefits, the Second IISC plans to newly add “Idea BBS” and “Audition” sections. Idea BBS is a website column, allowing applicants to find partners from SCN through online communication. Audition is a meeting, facilitating project owner to present idea and obtain assist from resource sponsors. It is expected that the promising projects will finally get resource and financial support based on the communication in both the Idea BBS and Audition sections.
